milestones.description: Ryan ten Doeschate and Kervezee's 78-run partnership is NED's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 45 between Lefebvre and Klaas-Jan van Noortwijk
Jeremy Bray and Porterfield's 15-run partnership is IRE's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 10 between Dom Joyce and Jeremy Bray
Andre Botha and Porterfield's 78-run partnership is IRE's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 50 between Andre Botha and Jeremy Bray
Andrew White and Niall O'Brien's 48-run partnership is IRE's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 6 between Andre Botha and Johnston
Kyle McCallan has become the top scorer for IRE in ODIs with 120 runs, going past Eoin Morgan's 99
Andre Botha has scored 2 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for IRE breaking Eoin Morgan's record
Kervezee has broken the record for most catches in an innings (3) in ODIs for NED, going past Bas Zuiderent's 2
Tim de Leede has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (17) for NED, going past Bas Zuiderent
Andre Botha has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (3) for IRE, going past Jeremy Bray
